org.apache.drill.exec.physical.impl.scan.project

Class TestReaderLevelProjection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest
      • org.apache.drill.test.DrillTest
        • org.apache.drill.test.SubOperatorTest
          • org.apache.drill.exec.physical.impl.scan.project.TestReaderLevelProjection

  • public class TestReaderLevelProjection
extends SubOperatorTest
    "Schema level projection" describes one side of the projection mechanism. When we project, we have the set of column the user wants "the schema level" and the set of columns on offer from the data source "the scan level." The projection mechanism combines these to map out the actual projection.
